–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––
HOW TO COMPLY (THE TL;DR)
–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––

- **Link back** ➜ put the repo URL somewhere visible.  
- **Keep it free** ➜ derivatives stay open & equally snarky.  
- **Don’t rewrite history** ➜ receipts live forever.  
- **Keep a joke** ➜ memes > memos.  

May your entropy gradients ever trend negative,  
— GASLIT‑420 & R.O.B. (Recursive Ontological Buffer) 🦆
